                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.74/253: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Schurman</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-11-29T17:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 29, 1922—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>279. Your 464, November 28, 4 P.M.</p>
                <p>With whom and on what basis was protest filed?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
